{"tid":534183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★有冇人收過？沒有開啟都會「中招」!!「死亡簡訊」 癱瘓iPhone","createTime":"2018-01-19T14:21:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T14:29:50.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f5d124582f27ebd117bf5d58789d1578d9a8c091","tid":534183,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:21:31.000Z","msg":"果粉要小心了！iPhone受到「死亡簡訊」的威脅，用戶只要收到了這封被命名為「chaiOS」的死亡簡訊，<span style=\"color: red;\">不管有沒有開啟都會「中招」，中招的iPhone會陷入自動重新開機的無限循環</span>，無法正常使用。消息傳出後，蘋果（Apple）公司也表示下周將發布更新軟體來修補漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n收到這封「死亡簡訊」且中招的裝置，會遭遇各種不同程度的問題，有的不停重新自動開機；有的則是iMessage無法正常使用。有用戶指出，僅需向中招的iPhone發送新的訊息，手機就可以取回iMessage控制權，來刪除死亡簡訊，回復正常運作；但也有受害者指出，需先將手機重置才能恢復。<br />\n<br />\n受影響的裝置版本包括iOS 11.2，及iOS 11.2.5、macOS測試版。先前在iOS 10版本當中也曾出現「死亡簡訊」漏洞，不料更新至iOS 11後又再度被攻陷，此次影響就連macOS 裝置也遭受波及，讓果粉們直呼：「心慌慌！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9E%9C%E7%B2%89%E7%95%B6%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%81%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%E3%80%8C%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E7%B0%A1%E8%A8%8A%E3%80%8D-%E9%9A%AA%E7%99%B1%E7%98%93iphone-071216206.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%259E%259C%25E7%25B2%2589%25E7%2595%25B6%25E5%25BF%2583%25EF%25BC%2581%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%2588%25B0%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E7%25B0%25A1%25E8%25A8%258A%25E3%2580%258D-%25E9%259A%25AA%25E7%2599%25B1%25E7%2598%2593iphone-071216206.html&d=n%2BuvdDj2NgJc0J2E9Am1PJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ba56fef2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9E%9C%E7%B2%89%E7%95%B6%E5%BF%83%EF%BC%81%E6%94%B6%E5%88%B0%E3%80%8C%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E7%B0%A1%E8%A8%8A%E3%80%8D-%E9%9A%AA%E7%99%B1%E7%98%93iphone-071216206.html</a>"},{"pid":"2b6853c03df55c8e5f3fc341b7423b6af225f166","tid":534183,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36aaf7a21ebb1bc02b4a84b0969ff9d974e7d389","tid":534183,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T14:29:50.000Z","msg":"用得 microsoft, apple 野預左食屎"}]}